casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Kenneth P. ANDRESEN.
No. D-2734.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 4, 2013.
Kenneth P. Andresen, of Charlotte, North Carolina, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
